        "richtext_ym3B7i": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Setting high standards for product performance and compatibility to offer a wider application and freedom to work and play while respecting our environment. Be free from grid reliance and start building the way of life you want. <br/><br/><strong>Sherpa was founded with people in mind</strong>, aiming to empower individuals through the delivery of high-quality, innovative power solutions. <br/><br/>We have observed the way the portable power market has evolved in recent years. With a growing demand for power and <strong>energy costs remaining high</strong>, there is a widespread desire for many to adopt a more energy efficient lifestyle, we have witnessed a substantial surge in the utilisation of portable power products in residential and commercial markets.</p><p>Aside from being a leisure solution, battery storage is gaining popularity as a practical means for individuals and businesses to <strong>save money</strong> and embrace energy ownership. </p><p>We believe in the value of versatile power solutions that<strong> eliminate the need for costly professional installations</strong>, and we are committed to reducing environmental impacts.</p><p><strong>We offer reliable customer service and expertise, along with affordable, sustainable solutions which are accessible to everyone.</strong></p>"
          }
